# Backend: use live site only

**There is no backend configured on this machine.** Do not start uvicorn, assume localhost, or run tests/scripts against 127.0.0.1.

- **API / debug / receipt tools:** Run against the **live site** only. Production URL: **https://r.alti2.de** (or the URL configured in CI/deploy).
- Scripts that call the API (e.g. fetch_ocr_from_web_tool.py, health checks, receipt analysis) must default to or use the live base URL, not localhost.
- Do not ask the user to "run the backend locally" or "start Docker." If you need API or OCR results, use the deployed site (and the secret/env the user has set there).
